1.prompt: Hi brad what can you do
1.output:
Hi there! I'm BRAD, a chatbot specializing in biology, bioinformatics, genetics, and data science. I can answer questions related to these fields to the best of my ability, and I have access to a text database for Retrieval Augmented Generation to augment my answers. Additionally, I can search the web for new articles, access Gene Ontology and Enrichr bioinformatics databases, run Snakemake and MATLAB pipelines, and analyze my own codes to provide more accurate and comprehensive answers. Please feel free to ask me any question you have!
